candidates.title: ⬆️ Bump libc from 0.2.97 to 0.2.134

labels.name: rust
labels.description: Pull requests that update Rust code

candidates.body:
Bumps [libc](https://github.com/rust-lang/libc) from 0.2.97 to 0.2.134.
Release notes

Sourced from libc's releases.

0.2.134

What's Changed

  • refactor: use grep -E instead of egrep by @​kxxt in rust-lang/libc#2916
  • Exposed malloc_size on Mac by @​naricc in rust-lang/libc#2921
  • fs: add NSFS_MAGIC constant by @​tammela in rust-lang/libc#2928
  • CPU_SETSIZE constant to dragonflybsd. by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2925
  • Update Docker image to Ubuntu 22.04 by @​JohnTitor in rust-lang/libc#2915
  • Use ::Option and not Option for pthread_jit_write_callback_t by @​thomcc in rust-lang/libc#2931
  • Prepare 0.2.134 release by @​JohnTitor in rust-lang/libc#2932

New Contributors

  • @​kxxt made their first contribution in rust-lang/libc#2916
  • @​naricc made their first contribution in rust-lang/libc#2921
  • @​tammela made their first contribution in rust-lang/libc#2928

Full Changelog: https://github.com/rust-lang/libc/compare/0.2.133...0.2.134

0.2.133

What's Changed

  • freebsd adding ptsname_r by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2878
  • openbsd: ignore ci error about unexistent KERN_NSELCOLL constant by @​semarie in rust-lang/libc#2879
  • Add ENOTSUP constant for riscv32/musl by @​kraj in rust-lang/libc#2884
  • freebsd cpuset affinity flags. by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2885
  • IEEE EUI-64 callss for freebsd/dragonflybsd. by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2882
  • apple SEEK_{DATA,HOLE} O_{EVTONLY,NOFOLLOW_ANY} by @​youknowone in rust-lang/libc#2886
  • Add confstr and guaranteed _CS_* constants on apple by @​thomcc in rust-lang/libc#2883
  • add freebsd's cpusetid_t api by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2887
  • Add CPU_SETSIZE const for FreeBSD by @​lwhsu in rust-lang/libc#2888
  • linux: add missing netfilter definitions by @​phi-gamma in rust-lang/libc#2876
  • Upgrade Ubuntu image on GHA to 22.04 by @​JohnTitor in rust-lang/libc#2890
  • add missing SOF_TIMESTAMPING flags by @​folkertdev in rust-lang/libc#2881
  • freebsd add shm_largepage_conf data and its ioctl request. by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2892
  • Add musl's lib folder to library search path by @​wesleywiser in rust-lang/libc#2893
  • linux: add rtnetlink mcast group definitions by @​phi-gamma in rust-lang/libc#2889
  • apple add pthread_jit_write_callback_t api related. by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2896
  • Fix the tests on the latest FreeBSD 14.0-CURRENT by @​asomers in rust-lang/libc#2898
  • Added missing constants from elf.h by @​paandahl in rust-lang/libc#2897
  • apple: Add the attrlist set of functions by @​beetrees in rust-lang/libc#2902
  • Add makedev for the BSDs by @​asomers in rust-lang/libc#2891
  • solarish SHM* flags by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2905
  • fcntl F_DUPFD_CLOEXEC has different values on Solaris and Illumos by @​gco in rust-lang/libc#2900
  • Solaris TCP_KEEPINTVL and TCP_KEEPCNT have wrong values by @​gco in rust-lang/libc#2901
  • Add new Linux system call constants by @​cd-work in rust-lang/libc#2904
  • openbsd: add getmntinfo(3) and getfsstat(2) support by @​semarie in rust-lang/libc#2907
  • Update s390x installer to 20220914 by @​JohnTitor in rust-lang/libc#2912
  • expose setgrent/getgrent/endgrent on fuchsia by @​SteveLauC in rust-lang/libc#2910
  • netbsd mcontext x86_64 constants. by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2911
  • Compatibility with ESP-IDF V5 by @​ivmarkov in rust-lang/libc#2913
  • linux add FICLONE* ioctl. by @​devnexen in rust-lang/libc#2899
  • Bump version to 0.2.133 by @​beetrees in rust-lang/libc#2906

... (truncated)

Commits
  • a2281d3 Auto merge of #2932 - JohnTitor:0.2.134, r=JohnTitor
  • 1c2ffa7 Prepare 0.2.134 release
  • e507572 Auto merge of #2931 - thomcc:option-root, r=JohnTitor
  • 1d7029a Use ::Option and not Option for pthread_jit_write_callback_t
  • 362960c Auto merge of #2915 - JohnTitor:road-to-jammy, r=JohnTitor
  • a119fdb Downgrade to Ubuntu 20.04 on sparc64
  • 737c37d Update sparc64 Debian image
  • 0233e88 Do not import sys/sendfile.h
  • 63cc149 Ignore some items
  • 6c91229 Auto merge of #2925 - devnexen:cpuset_size_dfbsd, r=JohnTitor
  • Additional commits viewable in compare view
